data.description: The Diplomat Beach Resort and Conference Center, a Curio Collection by Hilton, located between Miami and Fort Lauderdale, is an iconic beachfront destination that pairs ocean and waterway views with exceptional facilities and high-touch service. The flow and refined yet relaxed feel, are a breathtaking backdrop for getaways and gatherings of all sizes. Organized around a striking central glass tower, the thoughtful design links the beach through a series of dramatic pools and to a range of waterfront ballrooms and boardrooms conveniently connected to the hotel's grand atrium and gracious terraces. From exceptional meeting and dining facilities to expert event management services, to the world-class pool, spa and beach amenities – The Diplomat Beach Resort is a one-of-a-kind setting for unforgettable stays and events.
